Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm... This isn't a prank or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:25.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... as I thought... Minami likes Akihisa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm... This isn't a prank or anything!\NI'm seriously gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... as I thought... Minami likes Akihisa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi!! Mondai: hitori to{\i0}\N{\i1}futari docchi ga suteki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colorful mawari dasu watashi no shourai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doko made hanasou ka? Minai furi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Assou, ookina sekai{\i0}\N{\i1}wa kibun de hirogaru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kyou mo daisuki, hontou ni daisuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watashi no baka...{\i0}\N{\i1}Hoshi no kazu yori mo baka da{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunao ni narezu ni,{\i0}\N{\i1}kimi to aruku yume o mita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gomen ne... Datte!{\i0}\N{\i1}Koi to shiranakattanda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotaette kimi to nazo tasu{\i0}\N{\i1}watashi wa mugen no JUMP!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts 2-"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A week after the training camp, the{\i0}\N{\i1}Year 2 guys' suspension is over and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What is... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You were about to give me a\Nhead-butt. Of course, I'd dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a head-butt. It was a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Put your hands behind\Nyour head and explain slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Kissing... Joining our lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,A natural action for you and I since\Nwe made a promise to get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. I know kissing.\NWhat I wanna know is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,When, where, and with whom did you kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You got it wrong. I just know what it\Nmeans. It doesn't mean I experienced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die.\NWhat's with this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That... They were kissing a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... Akihisa is as stupid as ever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,He knew that that would\Nhappen if he kissed a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\Nwhile you were asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! I found another heretic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey! Stop it! I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey! Stop it! Ahhh!\N--...although I could only kiss him on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys! Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A court for passing final judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,And for the heretics...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,A punishment of death awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. We will now start the inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you doing here, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You got me dragged into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Read out the charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We will call the defendant,\NAkihisa Yoshii, "A,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,and Minami Shimada "Flat Chest."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A is charged with an act\Nof disloyalty to our doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,When A was sexually assaulting\NFlat Chest early this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,our fellow members captured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We will thoroughly investigate on the\Nrelationship between A and Flat Chest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,and take proper action on A as\Nwell as watch Flat Chest in the futu--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Just state the conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We're jealous that he was kissing a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The ruling is, death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akihisa, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't something ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,When'd you see Shimada\Nlast before this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it might've been the\Nlast night of the training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,After everyone fell asleep,\Nshe quietly came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you think it was strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I just assumed that she came to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what'd you say to her before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.57,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"To: Minami Shimada" "There's something I wanna\Ntalk to you about. Could you come to my room?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.94,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"To: Akihisa Yoshii"\N"Okay, but why at this late hour?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.32,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"To: Minami Shimada"\N"Isn't it obvious? I like what I like."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akihisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what'd you guys talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A love confession kinda thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,She confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I confessed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's ringing all sorts of bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Heretic Akihisa Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you repent your sin and accept the ruling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the ruling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sentencing you to\Na special bungee jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so that I know, what will I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,In order not to worry you\Nunnecessarily, I can only give you a hint,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's similar to\Nskydiving without a parachute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You're telling me exactly\Nwhat it is! So no cord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna make me\Nbungee jump without a cord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So... as I thought... Minami\Nlikes Akihisa... Minami likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! You're still like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii and Shimada just exchanged\Nwords through their eye contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And I thought I might\Nhave a chance with Flat Chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,If he's taken in not just Himeji\Nand Kinoshita but even Shimada,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki is the only one\Nwe have a chance with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.15,Main,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, is it okay if I sit at your table?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Mine is broken, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I guess it can't be helped.\NSure, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you clamming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... aren't we sitting too close?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,But the table is small, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Aki... Uhm, if you like, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...why don't we have lunch together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I made your lun--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Honey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't allow this damn\Npig to sit so close to you, Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,W-What can I do? My table is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so, it doesn't have\Nto be a pig that you sit with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,So as I thought, Minami likes Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But since Mizuki studies seriously,\NI don't want to bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,In Aki's case, even if I bother him,\Nhis grades are already bad, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I somehow get the impression\Nyou're badmouthing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't allow it! To think that\Nyou made lunch for this damn pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Fried chicken marinated\Nwith homemade sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,which you prepared after\Ngetting up at four in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The hamburgers that you made\Nwith expensive ground beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The potato salad made\Nwith organic vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the rice\Nhas a heart mark on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Miharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Miharu. I've been patient up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,but I want you to stop doing stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...because... I'm dating Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tatami {\i0}mat flip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is,\NMiharu. Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,No! I'll marry you and\Nname our daughter Mirai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,using one character from your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shimizu! What're you\Ngonna do if a boy is born?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Namihei is good enough if it's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Before that, Miharu and I can't make a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm starting the class now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Shimizu?\NGo back to your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here to deal with an important\Nmatter! Please overlook it this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,An important matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's very important that\NI annihilate the pigs in this classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm forbidding you to enter\Nthis classroom from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You're always at the center of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You have lots of stories to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it... It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. It looks like we're gonna\Nhave a big problem because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a movement within Class D\Nto try and start a Summoner Test War.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Whichever class Class D is trying\Nto fight is none of our concern, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if that's us, Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But our classroom\Nequipment is the worst ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no benefit for them\Nto attack... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Shimizu is\Ntrying to take things out on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,In order to separate you\Nand Shimada's seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,she's trying to switch our\Ntables back to cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:51.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to think that everyone\Nin Class D would agree with Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,We're the ringleaders\Nof the peeking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,All the girls think that we're their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,The Class D rep is Genji Hiraga,\Nbut he probably can't restrain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu, who's burning with jealousy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,and the girls, who're burning\Nwith anger towards the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of the suspension, the guys\Nhaven't been able to recover our scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though we have Himeji,\Nour forces aren't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There's only one way left...\NWe have to avoid the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's up to you and Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I wanna check, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:20.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you and Shimada really dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,As far as I remember, I don't think we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:30.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This is happening probably\Nbecause of an email I sent by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You sent an email by mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. What Akihisa did was bad enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,but Yuuji also made a blunder\Nwith incredibly bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what was going on... Sorry, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, if we clear\NShimada's misunderstanding and you two
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,go back to a normal relationship,\NShimizu will probably cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini, is there a wiretap\Ndevice Shimizu planted here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,There was, but I made it look\Nlike it was broken and removed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,About the email I sent you\Nwhile we were at the training camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...to tell you the truth,\Nyou got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's more like, I meant\Nto send it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sugawa, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! You were going to\Nconfess your love to Sugawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...! You may not act like it,\Nbut I thought you liked girls after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.30,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"To: Akihisa Yoshii"\N"Yoshii, why are you trying so desperately to peek on girls?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:32.67,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"To: Minami Shimada"\N"Isn't it obvious? I like what I like."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That's terrible in many senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Like I said, it was sent by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I see, I see... I thought it\Nwas a little, strange, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,but I finally understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You're careless, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't wanna be told that by you\Nwhen you sent it to the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna\Ndo about my first kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I meant no harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry doesn't cut it, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It was my first kiss, too,\Nso can it be considered even?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course it can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I-Is that right?\NWell, uhm... then thanks for the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Minami, I want you to\Nanswer me without getting upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You told Shimizu that we're dating.\NDoes that mean that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's... You know,\Nsince Miharu was persistent,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she might\Ngive up if I had a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And it was good timing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What a lame excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not being honest with herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you should've told me then.\NI thought you might like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,To see you acting meekly like that.\NAhh! My arm is getting dislocated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Now the confusion has been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, once we tell Shimizu about\Nthis, everything will be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the war with Class D was avoided.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The situation is now even\Nworse than it was this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm, is it true that you have pictures\Nof Akihisa in a sailor school uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,100 yen per pic. Redistribution is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have everything you have, plea--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Oops, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,That conversation {\i1}does{\i0}\Nsuggest a bad situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Akihisa. Don't\Nmake a fuss over trivial stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not trivial! Why are my pictures\Nbeing sold behind the scenes like Hideyoshi's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Akihisa! What you just\Nsaid is a bad situation for {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,How are things in Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,They're not aware of us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. We'll recover our scores while we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If they notice, we'll declare war right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... I thought Class D\Nwouldn't come to attack us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,No. This isn't Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,This conversation took place in Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk! That damn Nemoto! He really plays dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Why does Class B\Nwant to declare war on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems that his position was harmed\Nafter they lost the ST War against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they participated\Nin the peeking operation and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:19.17,Main,,0,0,0,,He's probably lost his\Nsay in matters in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,As a quick measure to control\Nthe complaints in Class B,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,he must be planning to create a new enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,By directing their anger at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,he'll get them to stop being angry at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,He probably wants to regain his lost ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! We haven't recovered our scores yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,If class B comes to attack us,\Nit's guaranteed we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to\Nthis, we have no choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.49,Main,,0,0,0,,but to create a situation where\NClass B can't declare war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All we need is for another\Nclass to declare war on us before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Having Class D declare war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! After we had just finally\Ncleared up Shimizu's misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and avoided a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,If we fight an ST War, we're given time\Nto recover our scores in recovery tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If we fight Class D, we can\Nrecover our scores without worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... If we take the test\Nand become fully prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Class B wouldn't come\Nattack us so easily, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But Yuuji, with our current scores,\Nwe can't even defeat Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,For that, I've got a separate solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, we'll provoke Class D\Nand have them declare war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll use what happened this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You and Shimada get cozy and instigate Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Definitely no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it's an act, there's no way I'd\Nbecome the girlfriend of such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimada, you're the only one who can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,If Class B attacks us now, we're\Ngonna go back to using cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,If that happens, Himeji's\Nparents will get worried again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,and could try to have her\Ntransferred to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to help us, too, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Shimada's acting by\Nitself would be unconvincing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We want you to act\Njealous of their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you somehow do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm, Minami, Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You may not want to do it, but please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that this is\Nmy own personal reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,but I really don't\Nwanna change schools, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. I just have to pretend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that that's been\Ndecided, let's just get right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... a script? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking you\Nto come see me like this, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been feeling the\Nsame all this time, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wh-what are these lines?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can say lines like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I know we're just acting,\Nbut it's too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.\NI'll show you an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking you to\Ncome see me like this, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ever since I met you for the\Nfirst time, I've been in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It was really hard for me to\Njust be a friend all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:24.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I couldn't bear staying just friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:32.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, I know it's strange to\Nsay this now after what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to tell you again.\NI'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,My heart went pitter-patter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Just for a bit... could you\Nleave me alone just for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,There are dreams that people\Ndon't wanna wake up from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini, put the wiretap\Ndevice on the rooftop back in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I want the three of you to go up\Nto the rooftop and put on a show
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,so that Shimizu will hear it through\Nthe wiretap device and get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The setup is that Akihisa and\NShimada are meeting secretly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Cross your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,In order also to make up for\Nyour earlier mistake, try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you if you\Ntouch me in a weird place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,If you cross it so tightly, it's hard to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We're dating, so this is just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Minami... they've been\Nhitting my elbow for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Y-You naughty jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Your ribs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! I have to keep acting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That's obvious, right? From head to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.04,Main,,0,0,0,,From head to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Fore... head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Being so close to each\Nother and even arm in arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks as if... you two are dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm? Was that line in the script?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I see! This is an adlib!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mizuki. Aki and I are dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sorry for not telling you, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So... as I thought, you like Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not telling you that,\Neither... when I knew how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You can't forgive me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I kinda knew how you felt, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:56.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I even feel better now that you've\Ntold me about it clearly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be that\Nyou're going to forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of\Nwhether I'll forgive you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you're free to like anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So I can't criticize you, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Mizuki... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But I won't forgive you\Nfor the kiss this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That was against the rules! On top\Nof that, that was Akihisa's first kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That was because of the\Nemail and stuff, so... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't "I just" me! Even if God forgives\Nyou for cheating like that, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's... a wiretap device?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You dummy, Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! If Himeji talks without noticing{\i0}\N{\i1}it and Shimizu figures out it's an act...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Aki! What's going on?\NDon't tell me you're choosing Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Minami! There's something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki! Stay here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I...! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There, I said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Shimada.\NDon't adlib carelessly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This is it. I'm done acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki likes girly girls\Nlike Mizuki anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I didn't notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Himeji? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Do I look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you somehow looked lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Looked lonely... huh?\NIf I do look like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,it might be because I felt sad that\Nthe person I like was taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...even if it was just an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Himeji.\NThat was just an act, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.\NIt was just an act, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I might be a little jealous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If there was a guy both you and\NMinami fall in love with, even if it's an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,If you really are in that kind\Nof situation, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Hmm... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll think really hard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll think really\Nhard about it in my own way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,and tell everything honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear who you'd pick, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How you were earlier.\NIt didn't look like you were acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...used to perform in plays or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hirameite, kagayaite, denkyuu pikkanko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinten shinai yo.{\i0}\N{\i1}Dareka jama shiteru... No, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zenzen tarinai, sore{\i0}\N{\i1}ga mondai no koubaisuu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryoukai sorenai. Nani ga{\i0}\N{\i1}hontou no koto... Baby?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:23:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mitetara koko de zukai shite yo, Baby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoba mo kazu mo kimi o arawasenai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kokoro ga biribiri{\i0}\N{\i1}suru S to N no jiryoku de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(S, S, Super kuttsuite{\i0}\N{\i1}Number, I say No. 1 boy!){\i0}
